By KAREEM YUSUF OLATAYO
This application makes use of itextsharp.dll library to generate
pdf file containing id cards of students seeting for WAEC
(West Africa Examination Council) in a school. The Automation
works compilina a list of students in a file using the name 
index of the list to fetch a related passport (picture) of the 
student.The application is indeed multi tasking and it also makes 
use of events and passes data between threads.
You can run the application with visual studio 2015 and above.
Enjoy and Happy Coding.